      <title>埃克森美孚在近三年后退出赤道几内亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/exxon-mobil-to-exit-equatorial-guinea-after-nearly-three-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司计划在几个月内撤离赤道几内亚，标志着近三十年的石油钻探活动的结束，该钻探活动使这个西非小国成为欧佩克成员国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/exxon-mobil-to-exit-equatorial-guinea-after-nearly-three-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:28:02 GMT</pubDate>
